cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper presents a speech to text transcription system using deep neural networks and language models. 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper deals with speech signal processing and transcription. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses transfer learning and semi-supervised learning techniques to improve the performance of the transcription system. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper uses unlabeled data from YouTube to improve the performance of the system, which can be considered as a social network. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep neural networks and language models, which are common techniques in the field of AI.
